        { "@type": "Question", "name": "What is Ubersuggest?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Ubersuggest is Neil Patel's all-in-one SEO tool that does keyword research, competitor analysis, site audits, backlink tracking, and rank monitoring. It is one of the cheapest entry-level SEO tools, starting at $29/mo with a lifetime deal available at $290 one-time." }},
