        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Does Ubersuggest write content for you?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "No. Ubersuggest is a pure research and analysis tool. It has no AI writing, no content editor, and no publishing capabilities. You need writers and a separate workflow to turn Ubersuggest data into published content." }},
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Is Ubersuggest worth it in 2026?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "For solo bloggers and beginners on a budget: yes. For agencies, in-house SEO teams, or anyone making decisions with real budget at stake: no — pay for Ahrefs or Semrush. The real monthly cost to run SEO with Ubersuggest data is $29 + $2,400–$7,500 for writers." }},
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "What are the best Ubersuggest alternatives?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Mangools ($49/mo) for cleaner UI at a similar price. Ahrefs ($129/mo) for the largest backlink index. Semrush ($139/mo) for all-in-one. For done-for-you content with publishing, theStacc ($99/mo) handles 30 articles and GBP posts per month." }},
